  Source:
    Title: Will You Sit With Me?
    By: Bonnie Myotai Treace
  Location:
    Page: 165
By: So Toba
Format: verse
---
The sound of the valley stream
is his great tongue,
The colors of the mountains
are his pure body.
In the night,
I have heard eighty-four thousand hymns,
But how to tell it to people
the next day?
